ology\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greek_mythology\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a take-off\", \"from\": 580, \"to\": 590}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 648}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the Paris scene, which featured drag queens and children, is juxtaposed with the Da Vinci masterpiece the similarity is striking.\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 719, \"end\": 724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998913154, \"rank\": 1.0887527938988624e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 796, \"end\": 804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.962875880945917e-35, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 763, \"to\": 771}, {\"ngram\": \"the similarity\", \"from\": 817, \"to\": 831}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A spokeswoman for the International Olympic Committee (IOC) issued a half-hearted 'apology,' stating that it was not intended to mock anything religious and that the IOC is sorry if anyone was offended.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"International Olympic Committee (IOC)\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 1012, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Intern