istianity\", \"score\": 0.9965497544316155, \"rank\": 0.0034075079303429634, \"text\": \"Christian Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this display\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Muslims, who revere Jesus as one of the greatest of the prophets, are also feeling insulted.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1464, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1372, \"end\": 1379, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"score\": 0.9999855341098228, \"rank\": 1.4466012160077532e-05, \"text\": \"Muslims\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islam\"}, {\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1397, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999981719156, \"rank\": 1.8282721497939644e-09, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prophets\", \"from\": 1424, \"to\": 1436}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In fact, many non-religious people have expressed disgust at these disrespectful antics.\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1553, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fact\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"many non-religious people\", \"from\": 1474, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"disgust\", \"from\": 1515, \"to\": 1522}, {\"ngram\": \"these disrespectful antics\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1552}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some have pointed out that that it's anti-woman and also that the hyper-sexualized twerking and gyrating of drag queens is hardly the right atmosphere to bring children into.\", \"from\": 1555, \"to\": 1729, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"woman\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1602}, {\"ngram\": \"the hyper-sexualized twerking\", \"from\": 1617, \"to\": 1646}, {\"ngram\": \"drag queens\", \"from\": 1663, \"to\": 1674}, {\"ngram\": \"the right atmosphere\", \"from\": 1685, \"to\": 1705}, {\"ngram\": \"children\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1723}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the cast actually had a 'wardrobe malfunction' that left his male genitalia exposed!\", \"from\": 1730, \"to\": 1821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the cast\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1745}, {\"ngram\": \"a 'wardrobe malfunction\", \"from\": 1759, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"his male genitalia\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When is the world going to say, 'enough is enough'?\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1874, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1840}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When will people see that this sort of spectacle only hurts your cause?\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1891}, {\"ngram\": \"this sort\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1910}, {\"ngram\": \"spectacle\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1923}, {\"ngram\": \"your cause\", \"from\": 1935, \"to\": 1945}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When will the IOC and TV networks smarten up?\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1992, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1964, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.841131719043451e-17, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Answer to that one: when enough advertisers pull their financial support.\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"enough advertisers\", \"from\": 2018, \"to\": 2036}, {\"ngram\": \"their financial support\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We could view this descent into the mire as an expression of cultural suicide.\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2146, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this descent\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"the mire\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"an expression\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"cultural suicide\", \"from\": 2129, \"to\": 2145}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By mocking Christianity people are turning their backs on our heritage in the Western world.\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999126873644, \"rank\": 8.731271044524235e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}, {\"begin\": 2225, \"end\": 2232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"score\": 0.4850957841955568, \"rank\": 0.8144056215317065, \"text\": \"Western\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Western_world\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their backs\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"our heritage\", \"from\": 2205, \"to\": 2217}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Christianity had a lot to do with giving us our form of government, our laws, modern science, the status of women, and much more.\", \"from\": 2240, \"to\": 2369, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2240, \"end\": 2252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.999999126873644, \"rank\": 8.731271044524235e-07, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2283}, {\"ngram\": \"our form\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"government\", \"from\": 2296, \"to\": 2306}, {\"ngram\": \"our laws\", \"from\": 2308, \"to\": 2316}, {\"ngram\": \"modern science\", \"from\": 2318, \"to\": 2332}, {\"ngram\": \"the status\", \"from\": 2334, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why are we so hell-bent on casting aside the moral wisdom of the last 2,000 years?\", \"from\": 2370, \"to\": 2452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the moral wisdom\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2427}, {\"ngram\": \"the last 2,000 years\", \"from\": 2431, \"to\": 2451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, we will regret the consequences for society if we continue on this course.\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the consequences\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"society\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"this course\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris 2024 brings to mind Paris 1924, the Olympics in which Eric Liddell, the Scottish sprinter, represented Britain.\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2536, \"end\": 2546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0906156008765279e-18, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2562, \"end\": 2572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999983342605, \"rank\": 1.6656582341219853e-09, \"text\": \"Paris 1924\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/1924_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2596, \"end\": 2608, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eric_Liddell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.0832373257641677e-46, \"text\": \"Eric Liddell\", \"types\": [